title: talk_francesco_intro
position: 300,0
group: francesco
color: blue
actor: ADULT_M
---
<<card cave>>
Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
Take a look at this machine — it's incredibly powerful!
<<action show_machine>>
Let me start it up...
<<action start_machine_fail>>
Wait... it's not working!
Something's wrong.
<<jump talk_antura_guilty>>
===

